\v 19 Bingelela uPriska\x + Seb. 18.2.\x* loAkwila\x + Seb. 18.2.\x*, lendlu kaOnesiforo\x + 1.16.\x*.
\v 20 UErastu\x + Roma 16.23.\x* wasala eKorinte\x + Seb. 18.1.\x*; kodwa uTrofimu\x + Seb. 20.4.\x* ngamtshiya eMilethu \x + Seb. 20.15,17.\x*egula.
\v 21 Khuthala\x + 4.9.\x* ufike ubusika bungakafiki. UYubulu uyakubingelela, loPudeni, loLino, loKlawudiya, labo bonke abazalwane.
